⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Mr. Jones
node AFM · AFM · ⟦Mr. Jones:AFM:1c65bd⟧

WHO   — Mr. Jones — the old order
WHAT  — The deposed tyrant whose cruelty justifies the revolt — and whose ghost the pigs invoke to justify their own rule.
WHERE — AFM · ANIMAL FARM  Framework inputs: Animal Farm (George Orwell, 1945)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the new order defines itself against the old, and ‘do you want Jones back?’ becomes the excuse for every abuse.
HOW   — By neglect, drink, and the whip — and, after his fall, by being the threat the pigs wave to keep the animals in line.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I was the drunk who starved them into revolt — and the pigs kept my name alive as the threat that justified becoming me.

spoken token : kraeth-brol-kor   ·   hex : 1c65bd
